TML보다 html 생성 속도가 10배 빨라진다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"파라미터-문법-구현-가능\" style=\"position:relative;\">파라미터 문법 구현 가능<a href=\"#%ED%8C%8C%EB%9D%BC%EB%AF%B8%ED%84%B0-%EB%AC%B8%EB%B2%95-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84-%EA%B0%80%EB%8A%A5\" aria-label=\"파라미터 문법 구현 가능 permalink\" class=\"anchor custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n        <div class=\"code-block-header\">\n          <span class=\"code-block-title\">javascript</span>\n          <button class=\"code-copy-btn\" aria-label=\"코드 복사\"><svg class=\"ico ico-code-copy\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 640\"><path d=\"M352 528H128c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V288c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16h48v-48h-48c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64v224c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h224c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64v-48h-48v48c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16m-64-160c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V128c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16h224c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16v224c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16zm-64-16c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h224c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V128c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64H288c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64z\"/></svg></button>\n        </div>\n      \n      <deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" terminal=\"none\" theme=\"base16-light\" line-numbers=\"true\">\n        <code slot=\"code\">class InputComponent extends HTMLElement {\n  connectedCallback() {\n    let name = this.getAttribute(&#x27;name&#x27;);\n    this.innerHTML = `&lt;label&gt;${name} 인풋입니다.&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input&gt;`;\n  }\n}\ncustomElements.define(&#x27;input-component&#x27;, InputComponent);</code>\n      </deckgo-highlight-code>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n        <div class=\"code-block-header\">\n          <span class=\"code-block-title\">html</span>\n          <button class=\"code-copy-btn\" aria-label=\"코드 복사\"><svg class=\"ico ico-code-copy\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 640\"><path d=\"M352 528H128c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V288c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16h48v-48h-48c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64v224c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h224c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64v-48h-48v48c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16m-64-160c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V128c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16h224c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16v224c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16zm-64-16c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h224c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V128c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64H288c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64z\"/></svg></button>\n        </div>\n      \n      <deckgo-highlight-code language=\"html\" terminal=\"none\" theme=\"base16-light\" line-numbers=\"true\">\n        <code slot=\"code\">&lt;input-component name=&#x27;비밀번호&#x27;&gt;&lt;/input-component&gt;</code>\n      </deckgo-highlight-code>\n    </div>\n<h2 id=\"attribute-변경-감지하기\" style=\"position:relative;\">attribute 변경 감지하기<a href=\"#attribute-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD-%EA%B0%90%EC%A7%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"attribute 변경 감지하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>attribute가 바뀌면, html도 자동으로 업데이트 해줄 수 있다.<br>\nname이라는 custom attribute가 변경될 때마다, 특정 코드를 실행할 수도 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n        <div class=\"code-block-header\">\n          <span class=\"code-block-title\">javascript</span>\n          <button class=\"code-copy-btn\" aria-label=\"코드 복사\"><svg class=\"ico ico-code-copy\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 640\"><path d=\"M352 528H128c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V288c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16h48v-48h-48c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64v224c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h224c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64v-48h-48v48c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16m-64-160c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V128c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16h224c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16v224c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16zm-64-16c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h224c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V128c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64H288c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64z\"/></svg></button>\n        </div>\n      \n      <deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" terminal=\"none\" theme=\"base16-light\" line-numbers=\"true\">\n        <code slot=\"code\">class InputComponent extends HTMLElement {\n  connectedCallback() {\n    let name = this.getAttribute(&#x27;name&#x27;);\n    this.innerHTML = `&lt;label&gt;${name}을 입력하세요.&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input&gt;`;\n  }\n  \n  static get observedAttributes() {\n    return [&#x27;name&#x27;];\n  }\n  \n  attributeChangedCallback() {\n    // attribute 변경 시 실행할 코드\n    this.innerHTML = `&lt;label&gt;${name}이 변경되었습니다.&lt;/label&gt;&lt;input&gt;`;\n  }\n}\ncustomElements.define(&#x27;input-component&#x27;, InputComponent);</code>\n      </deckgo-highlight-code>\n    </div>\n<h2 id=\"사용예시\" style=\"position:relative;\">사용예시<a href=\"#%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"사용예시 permalink\" class=\"anchor custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n        <div class=\"code-block-header\">\n          <span class=\"code-block-title\">html</span>\n          <button class=\"code-copy-btn\" aria-label=\"코드 복사\"><svg class=\"ico ico-code-copy\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 640\"><path d=\"M352 528H128c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V288c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16h48v-48h-48c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64v224c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h224c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64v-48h-48v48c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16m-64-160c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V128c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16h224c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16v224c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16zm-64-16c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h224c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V128c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64H288c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64z\"/></svg></button>\n        </div>\n      \n      <deckgo-highlight-code language=\"html\" terminal=\"none\" theme=\"base16-light\" line-numbers=\"true\">\n        <code slot=\"code\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\n&lt;html lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;\n&lt;head&gt;\n  &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;title&gt;Web Component&lt;/title&gt;\n  &lt;script type=&quot;module&quot; src=&quot;components/header-component.js&quot; defer&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n  &lt;!-- 헤더 컴포넌트 --&gt;\n  &lt;header-component&gt;&lt;/header-component&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;</code>\n      </deckgo-highlight-code>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n        <div class=\"code-block-header\">\n          <span class=\"code-block-title\">components/header-component.js</span>\n          <button class=\"code-copy-btn\" aria-label=\"코드 복사\"><svg class=\"ico ico-code-copy\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 640\"><path d=\"M352 528H128c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V288c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16h48v-48h-48c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64v224c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h224c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64v-48h-48v48c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16m-64-160c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V128c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16h224c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16v224c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16zm-64-16c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h224c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V128c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64H288c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64z\"/></svg></button>\n        </div>\n      \n      <deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" terminal=\"none\" theme=\"base16-light\" line-numbers=\"true\">\n        <code slot=\"code\">class HeaderComponent extends HTMLElement {\n  connectedCallback() {\n    this.innerHTML = `\n      &lt;header&gt;\n        &lt;nav&gt;\n          &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; id=&quot;home-link&quot;&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt;\n          &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; id=&quot;about-link&quot;&gt;About&lt;/a&gt;\n          &lt;a href=&quot;/contact&quot;&gt;Contact&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;/nav&gt;\n      &lt;/header&gt;\n    `;\n\n    this.addEventListener(&#x27;click&#x27;, (e) =&gt; {\n      e.preventDefault();\n      console.log(&#x27;click&#x27;);\n    });\n  }\n}\ncustomElements.define(&#x27;header-component&#x27;, HeaderComponent);</code>\n      </deckgo-highlight-code>\n    </div>\n<hr>\n<h5>참고</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://velog.io/@gil0127/Web-Components-%EC%BB%A4%EC%8A%A4%ED%85%80-HTML-%ED%83%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Web Components : 커스텀 HTML 태그 만들기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://velog.io/@rageboom/Custom-Elements\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">[웹 컴포넌트] Custom Elements</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/API/Window/customElements\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">MDN | Window.customElements</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_components\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">MDN | Web Components</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/API/Web_components\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">MDN | 웹 컴포넌트</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\">기본설명</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%B2%95\">기본 사용법</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%8F%85%EB%A6%BD%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B8-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EC%9E%90-%EC%A0%95%EC%9D%98-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C\">독립적인 사용자 정의 요소</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#built-in-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EC%9E%90-%EC%A0%95%EC%9D%98-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C\">Built-in 사용자 정의 요소</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%83%9D%EB%AA%85-%EC%A3%BC%EA%B8%B0-%EC%BD%9C%EB%B0%B1\">생명 주기 콜백</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#web-components-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Web Components 사용하기</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#html-%ED%83%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%A5%BC-innerhtml%EB%B3%B4%EB%8B%A4-%ED%9A%A8%EC%9C%A8%EC%A0%81%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%A7%9C%EA%B3%A0-%EC%8B%B6%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4\">HTML 태그를 innerHTML보다 효율적으로 짜고 싶다면</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%ED%8C%8C%EB%9D%BC%EB%AF%B8%ED%84%B0-%EB%AC%B8%EB%B2%95-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84-%EA%B0%80%EB%8A%A5\">파라미터 문법 구현 가능</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#attribute-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD-%EA%B0%90%EC%A7%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">attribute 변경 감지하기</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\">사용예시</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"gitLastModified":"2026.03.07"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[JavaScript] Web Components : Custom Elements","summary":"Custom Elements는 사용자 HTML Element를 만들게 해준다. 그리고 이는 DOM의 모든 기능을 다 사용할 수 있다. 기본적으로 두 가지 타입으로 생성한다.","date":"2026.03.04","categories":["JavaScript"],"author":["aluvy"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/b67cb563ea08a00c913235d3156997b4/8f3c3/cover.png","srcSet":"/static/b67cb563ea08a00c913235d3156997b4/5add7/cover.png 250w,\n/static/b67cb563ea08a00c913235d3156997b4/aef42/cover.png 500w,\n/static/b67cb563ea08a00c913235d3156997b4/8f3c3/cover.png 1000w","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/b67cb563ea08a00c913235d3156997b4/0b151/cover.webp 250w,\n/static/b67cb563ea08a00c913235d3156997b4/33dd0/cover.webp 500w,\n/static/b67cb563ea08a00c913235d3156997b4/6429b/cover.webp 1000w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1000px) 1000px, 100vw"}]},"width":1000,"height":1000}},"publicURL":"/static/b67cb563ea08a00c913235d3156997b4/cover.png"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/javascript/web-components-custom-events/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}